<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.7.2">
<l>paṇṭiva ṉāyaṉaṅkāy paṭiṟaṉpukun teṉmakaḷtaṉ</l>
<l>toṇṭaiyañ ceṅkaṉivāy nukarntāṉaiyu kantavaṉpiṉ</l>
<l>keṇṭaiyoṇ kaṇmiḷirak kiḷipōlmiḻaṟ ṟinaṭantu</l>
<l>vaṇṭamar kāṉalmalkum vayalālipu kuvarkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Once he was a herder, ladies. [After] the rogue arrived [here], my daughter,</l>
<l>Desiring the one who sipped her toṇṭai [fruit]-red lips,</l>
<l>Walking behind him, as [her] fish[-shaped] eyes shine, chattering like a parrot,</l>
<l>Are they setting out for Āli where bees settle in the paddy fields</l>
<l rend="indent">where the shore groves flourish?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
